{"article_id":"TLRM9aKGBnrnvFtp","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"U.S . Ambassador To Libya , Three Other Americans Killed In Benghazi Attack","depth":1},{"id":1,"text":"Update at 7:02 p.m . ET .","depth":6},{"id":2,"text":"The U.S. ambassador to Libya and three other staff members were killed in an attack against the American consulate in Benghazi , last night .","depth":9},{"id":3,"text":"The attack happened over an American-produced film","depth":10},{"id":4,"text":"that criticized the prophet Muhammad .","depth":10},{"id":5,"text":"-- Quoting U.S. officials ,","depth":11},{"id":6,"text":"the AP reports","depth":11},{"id":7,"text":"that the Pentagon is moving two warships toward the Libyan coast .","depth":10},{"id":8,"text":"CNN is also reporting the move .","depth":9},{"id":9,"text":"-- The remains of all four Americans","depth":9},{"id":10,"text":"killed in Libya","depth":9},{"id":11,"text":"have been recovered .","depth":8},{"id":12,"text":"-- American officials are `` reluctant to say , at this stage ,","depth":8},{"id":13,"text":"that this","depth":10},{"id":14,"text":"[ attack ]","depth":10},{"id":15,"text":"was planned . ''","depth":9},{"id":16,"text":"-- The State Department says","depth":9},{"id":17,"text":"this was `` clearly a complex attack . ''","depth":9},{"id":18,"text":"But it is still not clear what was going on outside the diplomatic compound at the time of the attack .","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"-- President Obama condemned the attack .","depth":9},{"id":20,"text":"`` There is absolutely no justification for this senseless violence .","depth":11},{"id":21,"text":"None , ''","depth":11},{"id":22,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":23,"text":"-- Republican presidential nominee Mitt Romney weighed in ,","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"criticizing a statement","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"issued by the State Department","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"calling for calm in both Libya and Egypt","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"and assuring Muslims","depth":12},{"id":28,"text":"that the American government condemned the film .","depth":12},{"id":29,"text":"-- The identity of the filmmaker is still largely a mystery .","depth":7},{"id":30,"text":"The U.S. ambassador to Libya and three of his staff members were killed in an attack on the American consulate in the country 's eastern city of Benghazi ,","depth":6},{"id":31,"text":"the White House confirmed Wednesday .","depth":6},{"id":32,"text":"The deaths of Ambassador Chris Stevens and the other embassy employees came","depth":7},{"id":33,"text":"after an angry mob surrounded the Benghazi consulate Tuesday night","depth":8},{"id":34,"text":"to protest a film","depth":10},{"id":35,"text":"ridiculing Islam 's Prophet Muhammad","depth":10},{"id":36,"text":"that had been promoted by an extreme anti-Muslim Egyptian Christian campaigner in the United States .","depth":9},{"id":37,"text":"The mob was armed with guns and rocket-propelled grenades ,","depth":8},{"id":38,"text":"according to The Associated Press ,","depth":8},{"id":39,"text":"but it was not immediately clear how the ambassador or the others were killed .","depth":7},{"id":40,"text":"President Obama on Wednesday reiterated the U.S. condemnation for the attacks `` in the strongest terms ''","depth":8},{"id":41,"text":"and vowed to `` work with the Libyan government","depth":10},{"id":42,"text":"to bring the killers to justice . '' `` There is absolutely no justification for this senseless violence .","depth":10},{"id":43,"text":"None , ''","depth":9},{"id":44,"text":"he said .","depth":7},{"id":45,"text":"The president said","depth":7},{"id":46,"text":"that the attack `` will not break the bonds between the United States and Libya . ''","depth":7},{"id":47,"text":"The State Department also named Sean Smith , a foreign service information management officer and 21-year diplomatic veteran , as among the dead .","depth":6},{"id":48,"text":"Release of the others ' names was awaiting notification of their next of kin ,","depth":7},{"id":49,"text":"the Department said .","depth":7},{"id":50,"text":"Secretary of State Hillary Clinton said Wednesday morning","depth":9},{"id":51,"text":"that U.S. and Libyan security personnel `` battled the attackers together '' during the assault .","depth":9},{"id":52,"text":"`` This is an attack","depth":11},{"id":53,"text":"that should shock the conscience of people of all faiths around the world , ''","depth":11},{"id":54,"text":"she said .","depth":10},{"id":55,"text":"`` There is no justification ...","depth":11},{"id":56,"text":"violence is no way","depth":12},{"id":57,"text":"to honor faith , ''","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"Clinton said .","depth":10},{"id":59,"text":"The State Department website says","depth":10},{"id":60,"text":"that Stevens is the sixth U.S. ambassador","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"to be killed by terrorists since 1968","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"and the first since 1979 .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"Stevens and Smith were among a group of embassy employees","depth":11},{"id":64,"text":"who had gone to the Benghazi consulate earlier","depth":13},{"id":65,"text":"to help evacuate staff there","depth":13},{"id":66,"text":"as the building came under attack by the armed mob ,","depth":12},{"id":67,"text":"the AP reports .","depth":10},{"id":68,"text":"Stevens , 52 , was a career diplomat","depth":14},{"id":69,"text":"who spoke Arabic and French","depth":14},{"id":70,"text":"and was the first U.S. envoy to the Libyan resistance ,","depth":14},{"id":71,"text":"which overthrew Moammar Gadhafi in 2011 .","depth":14},{"id":72,"text":"He was named ambassador earlier this year .","depth":12},{"id":73,"text":"NPR 's Michele Kelemen says","depth":13},{"id":74,"text":"Stevens was well known to journalists","depth":15},{"id":75,"text":"covering the region .","depth":15},{"id":76,"text":"`` He served in a lot of places in the Middle East , ''","depth":15},{"id":77,"text":"she says .","depth":15},{"id":78,"text":"`` This was his second tour in Libya .","depth":14},{"id":79,"text":"He played a key role in the uprising there .","depth":14},{"id":80,"text":"He was the U.S. envoy to the opposition in Benghazi","depth":15},{"id":81,"text":"when the opposition was fighting Col. Moammar Gadhafi , ''","depth":15},{"id":82,"text":"Kelemen says .","depth":14},{"id":83,"text":"NPR 's Greg Myre ,","depth":12},{"id":84,"text":"who was formerly based in Jerusalem ,","depth":12},{"id":85,"text":"has this personal remembrance of Stevens .","depth":11},{"id":86,"text":"In Egypt , hundreds of people","depth":12},{"id":87,"text":"protesting the film","depth":12},{"id":88,"text":"breached the walls of the U.S. Embassy in Cairo on Tuesday .","depth":11},{"id":89,"text":"The protesters tore down an American flag ,","depth":11},{"id":90,"text":"replacing it with a black Islamic banner .","depth":11},{"id":91,"text":"In a statement on Tuesday , the president said","depth":9},{"id":92,"text":"that he was directing `` all necessary resources","depth":10},{"id":93,"text":"to support the security of our personnel in Libya ,","depth":11},{"id":94,"text":"and to increase security at our diplomatic posts around the globe . ''","depth":11},{"id":95,"text":"NPR 's Tom Bowman reports","depth":9},{"id":96,"text":"that a contingent of U.S. Marines from the Fleet Antiterrorism Security Team , or FAST , was being dispatched to Benghazi .","depth":9},{"id":97,"text":"In his statement , President Obama said","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"Stevens and the others","depth":10},{"id":99,"text":"killed `` exemplified America 's commitment to freedom , justice , and partnership with nations and people around the globe ,","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"and stand in stark contrast to those","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"who callously took their lives . ''","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"In the first hours after the embassy attack","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"and before it was learned that Ambassador Stevens had been killed ,","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"Republican presidential hopeful Mitt Romney weighed in ,","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"criticizing a statement","depth":13},{"id":106,"text":"issued by the State Department","depth":13},{"id":107,"text":"calling for calm in both Libya and Egypt","depth":12},{"id":108,"text":"and assuring Muslims","depth":12},{"id":109,"text":"that the American government condemned the film .","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"Obama campaign spokesman Ben LaBolt responded","depth":9},{"id":111,"text":"that he was `` shocked '' in an email to the AP","depth":10},{"id":112,"text":"and that `` at a time","depth":12},{"id":113,"text":"when the United States of America is confronting the tragic death of our diplomatic officers in Libya ,","depth":12},{"id":114,"text":"Gov . Romney would choose to launch a political attack . ''","depth":11},{"id":115,"text":"On Wednesday , Romney stood by his remarks ,","depth":10},{"id":116,"text":"calling the State Department 's early statement `` inappropriate and disgraceful . ''","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"`` It 's terrible ... for America to stand in apology for our values , ''","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"Romney said","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"that the State Department issued the statement","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"as `` our grounds [ were ] being attacked and being breached . ''","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"But NPR 's Leila Fadel says","depth":12},{"id":123,"text":"the U.S. statement was issued at noon in Cairo ,","depth":13},{"id":124,"text":"long before protesters assaulted the embassy compound there","depth":14},{"id":125,"text":"or anyone was killed in Libya .","depth":14},{"id":126,"text":"( NPR 's Frank James has a detailed analysis about the campaign fallout on It 's All Politics . )","depth":11},{"id":127,"text":"Asked whether he might have spoken too soon about the events in Libya ,","depth":10},{"id":128,"text":"Romney said :","depth":11},{"id":129,"text":"`` I do n't think","depth":13},{"id":130,"text":"we ever hesitate","depth":13},{"id":131,"text":"when we see something","depth":13},{"id":132,"text":"that is a violation of our principles . ''","depth":13},{"id":133,"text":"Sen. John Kerry , D-Mass. , chairman of the Senate Foreign Relations Committee , said in apparent reference to Romney 's remarks","depth":9},{"id":134,"text":"that `` it is exactly the wrong time","depth":11},{"id":135,"text":"to throw political punches .","depth":11},{"id":136,"text":"It is a time","depth":11},{"id":137,"text":"to restore calm","depth":12},{"id":138,"text":"and proceed wisely . ''","depth":12},{"id":139,"text":"Sen. Jim DeMint , R-S.C. , in a statement on his website , defended Romney 's ,","depth":10},{"id":140,"text":"saying","depth":11},{"id":141,"text":"the GOP hopeful `` is absolutely right ,","depth":12},{"id":142,"text":"there is no justification for these deadly attacks","depth":13},{"id":143,"text":"and we should never apologize for American freedom . `","depth":13},{"id":144,"text":"` It was disheartening to hear the administration condemn Americans","depth":12},{"id":145,"text":"engaging in free speech","depth":13},{"id":146,"text":"that hurt the feelings of Muslims ,","depth":13},{"id":147,"text":"while real atrocities have been repeatedly committed by Islamic radicals against women , Christians , and Jews in the Middle East , ''","depth":11},{"id":148,"text":"he said .","depth":10},{"id":149,"text":"The California-based filmmaker Sam Bacile ,","depth":12},{"id":150,"text":"whose movie sparked the protests ,","depth":12},{"id":151,"text":"went into hiding Tuesday ,","depth":11},{"id":152,"text":"according to the AP .","depth":10},{"id":153,"text":"The two-hour film has been shown just once , earlier this year in Hollywood ,","depth":11},{"id":154,"text":"but a 13-minute English-language trailer of the film , Innocence of Muslims , was on YouTube .","depth":11},{"id":155,"text":"Bacile describes himself as an Israeli Jew .","depth":10},{"id":156,"text":"Two-Way colleague Eyder Perlata has a detailed take on the film and YouTube trailer","depth":9},{"id":157,"text":"that sparked the initial protests .","depth":9},{"id":158,"text":"The remains of all four Americans","depth":9},{"id":159,"text":"killed in Libya","depth":9},{"id":160,"text":"have been recovered ,","depth":8},{"id":161,"text":"says NPR 's Dina Temple-Raston ,","depth":8},{"id":162,"text":"who spoke with American officials familiar with the investigation into the events .","depth":8},{"id":163,"text":"The officials said","depth":7},{"id":164,"text":"that Ambassador Stevens ,","depth":9},{"id":165,"text":"who was based in Tripoli ,","depth":9},{"id":166,"text":"was visiting Benghazi for the opening of an American cultural center there .","depth":8},{"id":167,"text":"Temple-Raston reports","depth":9},{"id":168,"text":"that officials confirmed","depth":10},{"id":169,"text":"that members of Ansar al-Sharia , a militant group","depth":12},{"id":170,"text":"affiliated with Yemen-based Al-Qaida in the Arabian Peninsula ,","depth":12},{"id":171,"text":"were part of the mob","depth":12},{"id":172,"text":"that assaulted the Libyan consulate .","depth":12},{"id":173,"text":"It was not clear , however , whether the group 's involvement went any further .","depth":8},{"id":174,"text":"Ansar has denied","depth":8},{"id":175,"text":"it was behind the attacks .","depth":8},{"id":176,"text":"Temple-Raston 's sources are `` reluctant to say , at this stage ,","depth":7},{"id":177,"text":"that this [ attack ]","depth":8},{"id":178,"text":"was planned . ''","depth":8},{"id":179,"text":"The officials say","depth":5},{"id":180,"text":"there was no specific piece of intelligence","depth":7},{"id":181,"text":"suggesting","depth":8},{"id":182,"text":"that the consulate would be attacked ,","depth":8},{"id":183,"text":"but that a pattern","depth":8},{"id":184,"text":"observed in recent months","depth":8},{"id":185,"text":"suggested the possibility","depth":8},{"id":186,"text":"that someone or some group might be waiting for an opportunity","depth":9},{"id":187,"text":"to attack a U.S. target .","depth":9},{"id":188,"text":"National Security Council spokesman says","depth":5},{"id":189,"text":"it is too soon to know what the motive behind the attack was .","depth":5},{"id":190,"text":"`` There is a lot of press speculation","depth":8},{"id":191,"text":"for who did this and why","depth":8},{"id":192,"text":"but at this stage it would be premature to ascribe any motive to this reprehensible act , ''","depth":7},{"id":193,"text":"Tommy Vietor said in a statement .","depth":6},{"id":194,"text":"`` As the President said ,","depth":7},{"id":195,"text":"make no mistake ,","depth":7},{"id":196,"text":"we will work with the Libyan government","depth":7},{"id":197,"text":"to bring to justice the killers","depth":8},{"id":198,"text":"who attacked our people . ''","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":397,"left":0,"right":396,"relation":"organization","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":396,"left":355,"right":395,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":355,"left":237,"right":354,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":237,"left":227,"right":236,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":227,"left":209,"right":226,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":209,"left":1,"right":208,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":208,"left":205,"right":207,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":205,"left":201,"right":204,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":201,"left":2,"right":200,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":200,"left":3,"right":4,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":204,"left":203,"right":8,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":203,"left":202,"right":7,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":202,"left":5,"right":6,"relation":"mode","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":207,"left":206,"right":11,"relation":"same-unit","nu